Let the triangle have vertices $A$, $B$, and $C$, with $C$ being the right angle, and let the altitude from $A$ to the hypotenuse $BC$ have length $4\sqrt{2}$.  Then the base of the triangle is $AB$, and we have the diagram:

[asy]
